schools.name: Anna A. Borba Fundamental Elementary School

data.description: Back on the market with no fault to the seller. Welcome to this 3 unit income producing property in Chino. Located in a nice residential neighborhood within minutes to many local conveniences. Offering a front single family home with 3 bedrooms and 1.5 baths with AC and an attached 2 car garage built in 1997 and a 2 unit duplex in the back with alley access. 1 Unit is a 2 bed, 1.5 bath and the other unit is a 1 bed, 1 bath.  Original unit A was built in 1948 but added second attached unit in 1994. Deplex Units have newer roof and all have plus newer exterior paint. All 3 units provide long term, good tenants. Properties are professionally managed. Information deemed reliable but not guaranteed.
